             was indicted, for <rs id="t18220109-47-off234" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18220109-47-off234" type="offenceCategory" value="miscellaneous"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220109-47-off234" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pervertingJustice"></interp>
               that he, before the said felony, and burglary was committed, to wit, on the same day, feloniously and maliciously, did incite, move, procure, counsel, hire, and command the said 
                     <persName id="t18220109-47-person481">
                        Henry 
                        Brown
                     <interp inst="t18220109-47-person481" type="surname" value="Brown"></interp>
